+import { StyleSheet } from "react-native";
+import Colors from "../../../colors";
+
+
+const styles = StyleSheet.create({
+    container:
+        hei
+        marginTop:12,
+        justifyContent: 'center',
+        alignItems: 'center',
+    },
+    shadow:{
+        padding:20,
+        marginBottom: 6,
+        width: '90%',
+        height: 180,
+        backgroundColor: 'white',
+        borderRadius: 10,
+        shadowColor: '#000',
+        shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
+        shadowOpacity: 0.25,
+        shadowRadius: 3.84,
+        elevation: 5, 
+    },
+    header:{
+        flexDirection:"row",
+        justifyContent: 'space-between'
+    },
+    body:{
+
+    },
+    footer:{
+        flexDirection:"row",
+        marginTop:30,
+        alignItems: 'center'
+    },
+    dateTravel: {
+        marginLeft:20,
+    },
+    titleCard:{
+        fontSize:26,
+        marginBottom:20
+    },
+    btn_description:{
+        marginLeft:100
+    },
+    text_btn_description:{
+        fontSize:18
+    }
+
+});
+
+export default styles;
\ No newline at end of file
